ìíŸ@13b8d2c2c9268b0ea3f8dfeaa7f7a53bb67fd3daf7e395998d603e16c3d6762d⁄∂Title: This week in Nushell #250
Path: Nushell
Content:
kubouch initiated 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12960] Span ID Refactor - Step 1
 and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13101] fixed a test failure when running tests with nextest
.
WindSoilder 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13073] removed inner quotes once Nushell gets 
``=``
 sign in 
``run_external``
, used 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13056] pathdiff::diff_path to handle relative paths in 
``run_external.rs``
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13055] bumped version to 0.94.3
.
sholderbach 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13084] grouped 
``polars``
 crate updates in dependabot
, and moved 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13083] ``format date``
 to 
``Category::Strings``
.
devyn 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13044] added options for filtering the log output from 
``nu``
, increased 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13035] default compression level in msgpackz
, fixed 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13028] ``run_external::expand_glob()``
 to return PWD-relative paths
, fixed 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13027] external command name parsing with backslashes, and added tests
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13014] bumped version to 
``0.94.2``
.
rgwood 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13075] overhauled 
``explore``
 config
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13074] fixed 
``explore``
 panic on empty lists
, made 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12984] LS_COLORS functionality faster in 
``explore``
, especially on Windows
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12979] refactored 
``explore``
 cursor code
.
ayax79 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13069] upgraded to polars 0.40
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13043] fixed a couple of incorrect error messages
, and allowed 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13025] int values to be converted into floats
.
stormasm 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13067] reduced log tracing in nu-cli
.
abusch 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13047] made 
``query xml``
 return nodes in document order
, and tried 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13045] to preserve the ordering of elements in from toml
.
JoaoFidalgo1403 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12882] allowed stor insert and stor update to accept pipeline input
.
Decodetalkers 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13034] fixed a coredump without any messages
.
NotTheDr01ds 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13095] corrected an erroneous example in the 'touch' help
, and updated 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13068] ``cd``
/
``def --env``
 examples
.
Embers-of-the-Fire 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13032] made string related commands parse-time evaluatable
.
KAAtheWiseGit 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13018] used native toml datetime type in 
``to toml``
.
amtoine 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12998] completed the type of 
``--error-label``
 in 
``std assert``
 commands
.
IanManske 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12996] fixed display formatting for command type in 
``help commands``
.
roaldarbol 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12983] created 
``CITATION.cff``
.
hqsz 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12974] supported plus sign for "into filesize"
.
ymcx 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12898] fixed the colors when completing using a relative path
.
