íŸ@c28f217685ec875b75059566f2ab968835e72fdfa466954c8a6e9c88ee1de147⁄bTitle: This week in Nushell #250
Path: Nu_Scripts
Content:
maxim-uvarov 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nu_scripts/pull/873] proposed an improvement to 
``std bench``
, simplified the 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nu_scripts/pull/865] ``std bench``
 improvement candidate
, and offered a 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nu_scripts/pull/863] hotfix for 
``significant-digits``
 to not error if the input was 0
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nu_scripts/pull/862] updated 
``significant-digits``
 to not use string conversions
.
neur1n 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nu_scripts/pull/872] resolved several issues in nu_conda and nu_msvs
.
OJarrisonn 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nu_scripts/pull/871] updated rustup completions to use the new rustup help page style
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nu_scripts/pull/870] added 
``eza``
 completions
.
fdncred 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nu_scripts/pull/869] reverted "Add git coommit completions"
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nu_scripts/pull/868] originally added git commit completions then reverted
.
th-duvanel 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nu_scripts/pull/867] added docker completions
.
laisnuto 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nu_scripts/pull/866] completed git pull
.
zhangymPerson 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nu_scripts/pull/861] added docker aliases
.
